  <div class="row padding-top-10">
    <div class="col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1">
        <h3 class="left"> Directions</h3>
        <h3 class="gotham-thin left"> From Kailua</h3>
        <p class="left">
        From Kailua, head towards Kualoa Ranch and North Shore on Kamehameha Hwy. When you see a sign that reads 'Kualoa Ranch 1 mile', the venue will be half a mile on your right hand side. Look for the balloons gretting the entrance that says private 'kapu'. Turn into this driveway and follow the gravel road to Moli'i Gardens.</p>
        <h3 class="gotham-thin left"> From North Shore</h3>
        <p class="left">
        From the North Shore, head towards Kailua on Kamehameha Hwy. After passing Kualoa Ranch on your right-hand side, continue around the bend for a quarter mile. Look for the balloons greeting the entrance of a private driveway on your left. Turn down this driveway and follow the gravel road towards Moli'i Gardens.</p>

    </div>
